originalText.text: Sarah photographed my younger son's first birthday party at the little gym.  She was professional (in terms of responsiveness and showing up early on the day of), great-to-deal with, had good energy (was a positive addition to the party) and, most importantly, delivered wonderful family photos and photos of the birthday party in a timely fashion that were easily accessible.  Sarah also worked hard to get my kids to smile for photos, which was much appreciated (and can be challenging with toddlers and a new person).  I recommend!

originalText.text: It can be so overwhelming to begin a search for just the right photographer in NYC as there are so many.  In search of a photographer to take some photos of my 3 week old son, I stumbled across Natural Kids Photography's website and was so refreshed with the stye of work....Sarah departs from the super posy newborn photos you see that are full of props.  She works with natural lighting and looks to capture the pure beauty of your baby.  On the day of the shoot we were so impressed with Sarah, and are certain we have found the best choice for a family photographer.  As a first time mom I had quite a bit of anxiety going into the session as I was worried about how stressful it would be if the baby happened to be fussy that day...I can attest that there was no need to be worried as Sarah has such a calm demeanor and so much patience, completely surpassing my expectations.  The images we received back were STUNNING, she nailed it!!!  They were fresh, natural, and I am so thankful that we captured this moment in time.  We decided to secure a 6 month shoot and a 1 year shoot already as the experience we had was so positive, and the images so beautiful.  We highly recommend.
